snippet.title: Elden Ring - Hand Of Malenia Invader | PvP
snippet.description:
I was invaded by a Hand Of Malenia occupant, the weapon doesn't seem too good, easy to dodge and quite weak, I've tried it myself doesn't seem to be as useful as Malenia revealed to us.
